  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">If <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"the ordered pair x comma y \"></span></span> is the solution to the system of equations above, what is the value of&nbsp;<span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"3 x plus 3 y\"></span>&nbsp;</span>?</p>\n",
