  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. Subtracting the second equation, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"4 x minus 8 y, equals 9\"></span>, from the first equation, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"7 x minus 5 y, equals 4\"></span>, results in <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"open parenthesis, 7 x minus 5 y, close parenthesis, minus, open parenthesis, 4 x minus 8 y, close parenthesis, equals, 4 minus 9\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"7 x minus 5 y, minus 4 x, plus 8 y, equals 5\"></span>. Combining like terms on the left-hand side of this equation yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"3 x plus 3 y, equals negative 5\"></span>.<p>Choice A is incorrect and may result from miscalculating <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"4 minus 9 \"></span> as <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"negative 13\"></span>. Choice C is incorrect and may result from miscalculating <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"4 minus 9 \"></span> as 5. Choice D is incorrect and may result from adding 9 to 4 instead of subtracting 9 from 4.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
